# Notes
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# 1. Rules are applied in order - later rules override earlier ones
# 2. Use 999-local-overrides.mdc for project-specific exceptions
# 3. Some rules have alwaysApply: true (automatically loaded)
# 4. See rules/INDEX.md for complete rule catalog
# 5. Test your configuration by asking Cursor to generate code
